_sText:
The map that you see here is fy_scoutzglass, but with a big twist.
You are able to play the serious shooting each other game

OR

if you like hunting for secrets and want to spend your time doing that then you can do that.
There are approximately 10 or more secrets in this map ranging from a secret credit room to surf spots or laser dodging. This map helped me evlove my skills in the hammer editor.

There are still 8 spawns for each side
Totaling to 16 spawns in the map.
